<AWWayofTime:AlchemicalWizardrybloodRune:1>.addTooltip(format.aqua("Hold Shift for more Info"));
<AWWayofTime:AlchemicalWizardrybloodRune:1>.addShiftTooltip("This rune, when placed as an upgrade to the Blood Altar,");
<AWWayofTime:AlchemicalWizardrybloodRune:1>.addShiftTooltip("will increase the capacity of the main tank by 2 buckets.");
<AWWayofTime:AlchemicalWizardrybloodRune:1>.addShiftTooltip("This may not seem like much at first glance, but if you were");
<AWWayofTime:AlchemicalWizardrybloodRune:1>.addShiftTooltip("to use several slots of the altar on this rune you could easily");
