// Rune of Dislocation
<AWWayofTime:AlchemicalWizardrybloodRune:2>.addTooltip(format.aqua("Hold Shift for more Info"));
<AWWayofTime:AlchemicalWizardrybloodRune:2>.addShiftTooltip("In a nut shell, this rune speeds up the input and output");
<AWWayofTime:AlchemicalWizardrybloodRune:2>.addShiftTooltip("speeds of the fluid buffers. Per rune, the speed of the");
<AWWayofTime:AlchemicalWizardrybloodRune:2>.addShiftTooltip("buffer transfer will be 20% faster!");
<AWWayofTime:AlchemicalWizardrybloodRune:2>.addShiftTooltip("And since this effect stacks multiplicatively, the more ");
<AWWayofTime:AlchemicalWizardrybloodRune:2>.addShiftTooltip("runes you have the much faster it will drain!");

